    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/a448afe218b31aa3b2e1e8ee49fdfdcf.avif?t=1663675230\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>BLÖCK is an unforgiving and difficult precision 2D Platformer, which will demand a lot of patience and quick thinking from you.<br>The difficulty will raise exponentially throughout the unique levels of BLÖCK. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/7d8a8f8ac4a5b8ba87229f352b5f47dc.poster.avif?t=1663675230\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/7d8a8f8ac4a5b8ba87229f352b5f47dc.webm?t=1663675230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/7d8a8f8ac4a5b8ba87229f352b5f47dc.mp4?t=1663675230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>➤ 8 unique Levels, each with its own spectrum of colors.<br><br>➤ Earn in-game currency to upgrade the Speed, Jump Amount and Dash Power of your Player. <br><br>➤ Beat your own highscores and achieve max ratings on each level!<br><br>➤ Experience custom-made pixel art for each level.<br><br>➤ Enjoy the atmospehric and gameplay enhancing retro music.<br><br>➤ Dodge Lasers, jump over electricity and move fast when crossing ghost platforms!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/75b3e54b7d6a1edb918247cebcda6903.poster.avif?t=1663675230\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133540/extras/75b3e54b7d6a1edb918247cebcda6903.webm?t=1663675230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/